lead_paragraph: Britain came to the Olympics with high hopes and ended the swimming competition in the pool on Saturday with the country's best medal haul in more than a century and a determination to make even bigger waves in Tokyo in four years' time.

headline.main: Swimming: Britain Enjoys Best Haul in Century
